| Option | Effect | Duration |
|--------|--------|----------|
| Kybella | Dissolves fat | Permanent |
| Morpheus8 | RF tightening | 1-2 years |
| Ultherapy | Ultrasound tightening | 1-2 years |
| Botox (neck bands) | Relaxes bands | 3-4 months |

