**Facelift + Fat Transfer**
- Lift plus volume restoration
- Natural enhancement
- Addresses deflation + sagging
- More complete result

**Full Facial Rejuvenation:**
- Facelift + neck lift + bleph + fat transfer
- "One and done" approach
- Single recovery period
- Comprehensive result
- Longer surgery (4-6+ hours)

**Staging vs All At Once:**

| Approach | Pros | Cons |
|----------|------|------|
| All at once | Single recovery, comprehensive | Longer surgery, more risk |
| Staged | Shorter surgeries, lower risk | Multiple recoveries, higher total cost |

**What Most Surgeons Recommend:**
If procedures complement each other and you're healthy enough for longer surgery, doing them together makes sense. But listen to your surgeon's assessment.`,
